'''Metis'''
#''(Greek Mythology)'' The personification of "Wisdom". Daughter of the [[Titan]]s [[Oceanus]] and [[Tethys]]. She was a Titan, but not one of the first twelve Titans. First spouse of [[Zeus]], and the mother of [[Athena]], goddess of wisdom. She symbolises the divine wisdom.
# a [[satellite]] of [[Jupiter]]
# a band of part Native American, part Caucasian peoples who inhabited Southern Manitoba in Canada.


